  "body": "EDITOR UPDATE (2017-08-15): This EIP is now located at https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/blob/master/EIPS/eip-160.md. Please go there for the correct specification. The text below may be incorrect or outdated, and is not maintained.\r\n-----\r\n\r\n### Specification\r\n\r\nIf `block.number >= FORK_BLKNUM`, increase the gas cost of EXP from 10 + 10 per byte in the exponent to 10 + 50 per byte in the exponent.\r\n### Rationale\r\n\r\nBenchmarks suggest that EXP is currently underpriced by a factor of about 4-8.\r\n",
